Many Logitech input peripherals - mostly mouse and keyboards, but also numpads, presenters, trackballs and touchpads - come with a unique USB receiver. If your peripherals and receiver are not paired from fabric, but support the [http://support.logitech.com/en_us/software/unifying Logitech Unifying technology], you can still pair them using the {{Package|app-misc/ltunify}} package.

The package is available for {{Keyword|~amd64}} and {{Keyword|~x86}} only.

