== Usage ==
The usage is trivial.

{{RootCmd|ltunify list}}

shows the devices actually paired.

{{RootCmd|ltunify unpair idx}}

removes a listed paired devices that doesn't exist anymore.

{{RootCmd|ltunify pair}}

add a device simply asking to switch it off and on.

{{RootCmd|ltunify --help}}

shows a complete help.

